{"tid":1762163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果：【抗暴之戰●茂名】實名制+人臉識別下抗爭 市民收警方短訊：有個資同罪名","createTime":"2019-11-29T11:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T09:02:53.000Z","uid":318876,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbd082bbf546b5656b202fd8dcf9a3063fe7bc4","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEGshGr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEGshGr.jpg&h=7d499260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東茂名化州市文樓鎮市民不滿政府徵地興建火葬場，連續2日上街抗爭。當地有市民爆出，已收到警方訊息，其中清楚列出她的罪名、身份證號碼資料等。<br />\n<br />\n這條訊息完整內容為：「化州警方嚴重警告：XXX（抗爭者全名），身份號號碼：XXXXXXXXXXX，你11月28日在文樓鎮實施衝擊政府機關、扔汽油彈、用石頭打無人機等違法罪名已被公安機關掌握在案，請立即停止違法行為，否則將被從嚴追究刑事責任。」<br />\n<br />\n在內地，衣食住行都離不開實名制，上網、打電話如是。在實名制配合人臉識別系統的大環境下，抗爭者實行公民抗爭的應有權利，更見困境。目前茂名居民仍在抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2ae8252ea9fa9b106f52133c7f97911cece6c9","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"13c62c5bb650e7d27cfb1a711b77c43eccdb5f38","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1f11b1c0158367b343bce680548bc11641aa5028","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"9bc0a595344e7550844eb647845ff15605236a96","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c73397c21ae308668e36b6c662adce3f371f4319","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"97e71e7832fbd03c30b2179f9e7159028abd0a61","tid":1762163,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"26c544bf089b